‘If things don’t change then ultimately Brendan will pay the price,’ said Nicol. 

‘If this team keeps performing the way they are, I don’t think they’ll have another option. We are not even halfway through and most people don’t expect Liverpool to get into the top four.

‘You wonder where this team are going. He has tried to add to the squad to make it better. Somehow it has turned the other way. 

